flowchart LR
    User["Developer or product reviewer"]

    subgraph Mobile["Flutter mobile app"]
        App["<<component>> Product app"]
        Wrapper["<<component>> Codex dev wrapper"]
        Workbench["<<component>> SDD visual workbench"]
        DiagramViewer["<<component>> Mermaid diagram viewer"]
        FeedbackCapture["<<component>> Feedback capture"]
    end

    subgraph Backend["Configured Bridge backend"]
        SddApi["<<component>> Read-only SDD API"]
        FeedbackApi["<<component>> Feedback API"]
        ActionApi["<<component>> Codex action API"]
        SddService["<<component>> SddProjectService"]
    end

    subgraph Workspace["Current workspace"]
        Manifest["<<component>> codex-bridge.yaml"]
        Specs["<<component>> specs/<feature>/*.md"]
        Architecture["<<component>> architecture/*.mmd"]
        FeatureDiagrams["<<component>> specs/*/diagrams/*.mmd"]
        RealConfig["<<component>> Real release config"]
    end

    subgraph Tooling["Developer tooling"]
        Codex["<<component>> Codex CLI workflows"]
        Doctor["<<component>> SDD doctor"]
    end

    User --> App
    App -->|Flutter builder| Wrapper
    Wrapper -->|Workbench entry| Workbench
    Workbench -->|Mermaid preview| DiagramViewer
    Workbench -->|HTTP SDD API| SddApi
    Workbench -->|HTTP feedback API| FeedbackApi
    Workbench -->|HTTP action API| ActionApi
    FeedbackCapture -->|HTTP feedback API| FeedbackApi
    SddApi -->|service call| SddService
    SddService -->|file read| Manifest
    SddService -->|file read| Specs
    SddService -->|file read| Architecture
    SddService -->|file read| FeatureDiagrams
    SddService -->|file read| RealConfig
    ActionApi -->|Codex workflow| Codex
    ActionApi -->|doctor command| Doctor

    %% UML interface orientation: consumer is on the circle side; provider is on the C/socket side.
    %% uml-interface: Flutter builder consumer=App provider=Wrapper
    %% uml-interface: Workbench entry consumer=Wrapper provider=Workbench
    %% uml-interface: Mermaid preview consumer=Workbench provider=DiagramViewer
    %% uml-interface: HTTP SDD API consumer=Workbench provider=SddApi
    %% uml-interface: HTTP feedback API consumer=Workbench provider=FeedbackApi
    %% uml-interface: HTTP action API consumer=Workbench provider=ActionApi
    %% uml-interface: Codex workflow consumer=ActionApi provider=Codex
